---
// Banner que conecta el fichaje con el ecosistema Rapidgest ERP.
---

<section
    class="py-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-blue to-brand-blue-hover relative overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
        <div
            class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-brand-green rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-60 h-60 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 text-center md:text-left"
        >
            <div class="flex-1">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-xs font-semibold text-white mb-4"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-3.5 h-3.5"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        ><path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
                    >
                    Parte de Rapidgest
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight"
                >
                    No es solo fichaje. Es mucho más.
                </h3>
                <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    El módulo de fichaje está integrado en <strong
                        class="text-white">Rapidgest</strong
                    >. Conecta las horas trabajadas directamente con tus
                    nóminas, facturación/Verifactu y gestión de proyectos. Todo en una
                    sola plataforma.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="shrink-0">
                <a
                    href="https://rapidgest.com/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-brand-blue font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
                >
                    Conocer Rapidgest
                    <svg
                        class="w-4 h-4"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        ><path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
